name: The Pond-Wisp Camellians
description: Receiving aid from the Mohoe in a time of great need, the The Pond-Wisp Camellians were left with a deep seated gratitude towards the Mohoe. They're also known for their exceptional candescent flashmarble craftsmanship. Now finished uncovering the origin of the Clouddrop wisps, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
